text: Priit Sibul in 2015 Priit Sibul (born 31 December 1977 in Valga) is an Estonian politician, member of the Riigikogu, and Secretary General of Pro Patria and Res Publica Union. ==References== Category:Estonian politicians Category:Members of the Riigikogu Category:Isamaa politicians Category:People from Valga, Estonia Category:1977 births Category:21st-century Estonian politicians Category:Living people
